::KitKat::

She turned her head to look at Quickstrike. "Yes. I know about 
Megatron. We are currently working together."

She stood up from her seat and looked at Quickstrike. "And Aracnia is 
working with myself and Megatron as well. We are going to work 
together to crush the Allience."  She put a hand on his shoulder."Do 
not worry. I remember what Megatron is capable of. I know how he 
thinks. I won't let him hurt you or Darkmouse or anyone. I'd rather 
have him kill me than let harm come to any of you."

She walked past Quickstrike and opened the landing doors. "OK, 
Everyone out."

She opened her link "Destructor, we are here, please come and meet 
us."
